# 📅 Day 16 – Correlated Subqueries

## Topics Covered

- Correlated Subqueries

## Brief Explanation

The inner query depends on the outer query.

### Example

```sql
SELECT name
FROM Employees e
WHERE salary >
(
SELECT AVG(salary)
FROM Employees
WHERE dept = e.dept
);
```

